## NordVPN (Install)

With NordVPN, encrypt your online activity to protect your private data from hackers or snoopy advertisers. Enjoy global connectivity along with high-performance speed and secure access to streaming websites, censored content and social networks.

**SOCIAL MEDIA:**
[Facebook](https://www.facebook.com/NordVPN) | [Twitter / X](https://twitter.com/NordVPN) | [YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/c/NordVPN)

**OTHER NORD PRODUCTS:**
[NordPass](https://chocolatey.org/packages/nordpass) | [NordLayer (Teams)](https://chocolatey.org/packages/nordvpn-teams)

#### choco://nordvpn

To use choco:// protocol URLs, install [(unofficial) choco:// Protocol support](https://chocolatey.org/packages/choco-protocol-support)

### Package-specific issue

If this package isn't up-to-date for some days, [create an issue](https://github.com/arrrghhh/ChocolateyPackages/issues/new/choose)

